                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 5747/13.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Squiers</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Panama</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1908-04-09">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 9, 1908</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Squiers reports that the minister for foreign affairs approves the
                    suggestion and will instruct Minister Arango to take up the matter with the
                    department.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
